text: It Ain't My Fault or Ain't My Fault may refer to: *"It Ain't My Fault" (Silkk the Shocker song), 1998 *"It Ain't My Fault" (Brothers Osborne song), 2017 *"Ain't My Fault", a 2016 song by Zara Larsson *"Ain't My Fault", a 2014 song by Mitch Goudy *"Ain't My Fault", a 2015 song by Jamie Foxx from the album Hollywood: A Story of a Dozen Roses
title: It Ain't My Fault
